  "instructions": [
    "In a wok or large skillet, heat some oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and onions. Sauté until the garlic is golden brown and onion softens.",
    "Push the vegetables to one side of the pan and add flat rice noodles on the other side. Stir-fry for 1-2 minutes, then mix everything together evenly.",
    "Add sliced green bell pepper and stir-fry for an additional minute.",
    "Stir in chopped cilantro leaves and a pinch each of salt and black pepper. Mix well to combine.",
    "Serve hot as a solo dinner dish."
